Package org.cloudgraph.store.key

Contains common row and column key creation related interfaces and utilities applicable to most key/value data stores.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GraphColumnKeyFactory
    Generates a column key based on the configured CloudGraph column key model for a specific table configuration.
    GraphRowKeyExpressionFactory
    Generates a row key based on the configured CloudGraph row key model for a specific table configuration.
    GraphRowKeyFactory
    Generates an data store row key based on the configured CloudGraph row key model for a specific HTable configuration.
    GraphStatefullColumnKeyFactory
    Generates a column key based on the configured CloudGraph column key model for a specific table configuration.
    MetaField  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KeyValue
    Associates an SDO property with a data value and optional path to the property from a given context root.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EdgeMetaField
    Fields used to describe a set or collection of edges used to find and de-reference local or remote entities.
    EntityMetaField
    Fields used to describe an "entity" or instance of some type within a graph.
    GraphMetaField
    Fields used to describe a graph/row.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    GraphKeyException  
    KeyException  
    KeyFieldOverflowException
    Used when data for a composite row or column key field exceeds the defined size of the field.
    RequiredKeyFieldException
